112
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:57,920
Thank you.

113
00:08:02,519 --> 00:08:04,759
Do you know
why I chose to study medicine?

114
00:08:07,519 --> 00:08:08,800
I often hoped

115
00:08:09,839 --> 00:08:14,560
