saved my father back then.

116
00:08:39,879 --> 00:08:41,080
Let me lean on you for a second.

117
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:53,559
Can you hold me?

118
00:09:13,559 --> 00:09:15,840
I'm only pretending to be tough.

119
00:09:17,279 --> 00:09:17,879
In fact,

120
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:19,679
I've missed my dad.

121
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:23,360
When I see other people's dads,

122
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:25,840
I am reminded of my own.

123
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:28,080
How I wish he is still alive.

